para_trans: Hon'ble Speaker, regarding the allotment of Government Bungalow to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly.
Shri Rahul Suresh Navekar, Hon'ble Speaker, Maharashtra Legislative Assembly as "Sivagiri" Narayan
The government has decided to allot government bungalows at Dabholkar Marg, Malabar Hill, Mumbai.
2. Distributed by the Hon'ble Speaker, Maharashtra Legislative Assembly after his discharge from office.
It will be mandatory to vacate the residence within a period of fifteen days.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
